snippet.title: Fantasy Legion - Strategy Puzzle Game - Spell Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for a brand new army vs army battle where strategy matters! Spells are now available to cast in the battlefield. Cast wisely and it will turn the tide of a battle!
